---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="CIA">
<section id="experience" class="section-pad">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">CTF History</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Battle-<span>Tested</span></h2>
    <p class="section-desc">A growing record of competitions that shaped who we are.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">2025-2026 Run</span>
        <span class="tl-place">National + Global</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">Breakthrough Run — #49 Global</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">Competed in 70+ events across national and international circuits, accumulating 349.718 rating points and securing our best ranking yet: #49 globally and 3rd in Bangladesh on CTFtime.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag">70+ CTFs</span>
        <span class="tl-tag">349.718 pts</span>
        <span class="tl-tag pink">#49 Global</span>
        <span class="tl-tag amber">#3 Bangladesh</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">UMDCTF 2026</span>
        <span class="tl-place">University of Maryland</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">14th Place, Open Division — 49.949 pts</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">One of our strongest individual performances. Scored 2,193 points at UMDCTF 2026, placing 14th in the Open Division out of 743 teams and earning nearly 50 rating points.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag">2193 CTF pts</span>
        <span class="tl-tag pink">49.949 rating pts</span>
        <span class="tl-tag indigo">Top 15</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">TAMUctf 2026</span>
        <span class="tl-place">Texas A&amp;M University</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">91st Place — 54.849 pts</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">Our highest single-event rating point haul in 2026. Solved challenges across multiple categories earning 1,430 CTF points and 54.849 rating points.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag">1430 CTF pts</span>
        <span class="tl-tag amber">54.849 rating pts</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">BUET CTF 2026</span>
        <span class="tl-place">National · Bangladesh</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">7th Place — National Breakout</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">Finished 7th at BUET CTF 2026, one of the biggest national CTFs in Bangladesh, marking one of our strongest domestic results.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag pink">#7 Finish</span>
        <span class="tl-tag amber">National CTF</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">CUET CTF 2025</span>
        <span class="tl-place">National · Bangladesh</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">11th Place — Strong National Showing</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">Placed 11th in CUET CTF 2025, another major national event, proving the team could compete consistently across Bangladesh's top university CTFs.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag">#11 Finish</span>
        <span class="tl-tag indigo">National CTF</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">V1t CTF 2025</span>
        <span class="tl-place">Season Highlight</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">20th Place — Breakout International Push</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">Secured 20th place at V1t CTF 2025, one of the defining results from our debut year and an early sign that CIA could punch above its age.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag amber">#20 Finish</span>
        <span class="tl-tag">2025 Highlight</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="tl-meta">
        <span class="tl-year">2025 Season</span>
        <span class="tl-place">Global · First Year</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tl-title">Origin — Team Founded at BUP</h3>
      <p class="tl-desc">CIA was born in 2025 from a small group of BUP students. That first season established our national presence with standout finishes at V1t and CUET, setting up the climb that later took us to #3 in Bangladesh.</p>
      <div class="tl-tags">
        <span class="tl-tag">98.599 pts</span>
        <span class="tl-tag pink">#645 Global</span>
        <span class="tl-tag indigo">#11 Bangladesh</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
